#834
An Old Veteran's Home~
The room is quite spacious and made entirely of stone.  A large hearth
burns brightly in the eastern wall, heating the area.  Thick rugs made
of bear and deer hide cover the hardwood floor and hang from the walls.
Large foot lockers made of iron and copper line the walls.
