#907
A Dead-End~
A narrow alley from the south has opened up into this ten by ten foot
courtyard. Tall stone walls of buildings rise up to the north, east
and west.  No windows face into this courtyard.  Garbage and debris
clutter the area, stacked high against the walls.  A large crate stands
against the northern wall.
~
