#7101
Atop a Stone Pillar~
You are perched on a massive stone pillar, apparently carved from black
granite. It is approximately ten feet in diameter and twenty feet tall.
Stretching out in all directions below you in a thriving town.  Beyond
the walls of the city is a vast forest.  A staircase, blending into the side
of the pillar, leads down to the town square.
~
