#7102
Town Square~
This is a large, open square in the center of town.  The ground is paved
with worn down cobblestones.  The surrounding buildings are made mostly
from heavy timber and brick, and a few of the more prominent buildings
are constructed of stone and marble.  Wide, heavily used streets lead in
each of the four cardinal directions.
In the center of the square is an immense pillar of black granite.  Steps
have been carved into the sides, spiraling upward twenty feet to the top.
Arcane runes are etched into the pillar's surface and filled with molten
silver.
~
