#7111
The Adventurers' Guild~
From the looks of your surroundings, you are in a large, one-room building.
The floor is polished hardwood and the walls are a combination of brick
and roughly finished stones.  Several tables and many chairs have been
placed all around the room.  Various maps are pinned to the walls,
displaying the city and surrounding areas.  Open doorways provide exits to
the east and south.  In the northwest corner of the room, you notice an
open trapdoor in the floor.
~
