#7157
The Recovery Room~
You have entered a local bar known as The Recovery Room.  A long bar
occupies the north wall, behind which is a huge mirror.  Many stools have
been set up in front of it and tables and chairs cover most of the
remaining floor space.  Towns people, merchants, bards and all sorts of
others crowd this place.  The noise level seems to have risen since you
arrived and you have the strong urge to settle in and drink yourself
unconscious.
~
