At the Water-wheel~
You are walking through the underbrush surrounding the walls of New
Genesia. The town's wall is to the east, only a few feet away.  A
small stream cuts across the path from the west and proceeds to flow
south along the wall.  Attached to the wall at this spot is a water-wheel,
being turned by the quickly flowing stream.  It appears to be pumping
water into the city.
